title: VERBATIM: A young Kennedy delivers Dems' response to Trump
text:
VERBATIM: A young Kennedy delivers Dems' response to Trump Wednesday, January 31, 2018 - 01:07 
Congressman Joseph Kennedy III , the grandson of Robert F. Kennedy, delivers the official Democratic response to President Trump's State of the Union address.   
Congressman Joseph Kennedy III , the grandson of Robert F. Kennedy, delivers the official Democratic response to President Trump's State of the Union address.  //reut.rs/2DQmu3j
